# Configuração para OCI Resource Scheduler (Oracle Cloud Console)
#
# 1. Console Oracle → Developer Services → Resource Scheduler → Create schedule
# 2. Nome: newsletter-daily-8am
# 3. Schedule type: Cron expression
# 4. Cron: 0 8 * * *  (todo dia às 8h UTC — ajuste conforme fuso desejado)
#    Para 8h Brasília (UTC-3): 0 11 * * *
# 5. Action type: HTTP request (Functions ou invoke via API Gateway)
#
# Alternativa mais simples: use o crontab na própria VM:
#   ADMIN_TOKEN=xxx ./deploy/install-crontab.sh
#
# Ou configure uma OCI Function que executa:
#   curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $ADMIN_TOKEN" https://techndevn.com/trigger-email
#
NEWSLETTER_URL=https://techndevn.com
ADMIN_TOKEN=defina_o_mesmo_valor_do_env
